## Interactive chat loop
Run this cell, type messages, enter `exit` to stop.
print("Finance AI Bot — type your message, 'exit' to quit\n")

while True:
    try:
        message = input("You: ").strip()
    except (EOFError, KeyboardInterrupt):
        print("\nStopped.")
        break

    if not message:
        continue
    if message.lower() == "exit":
        print("Bye.")
        break

    result = run_analysis(message=message, user_id="dev")
    print(f"\nBot: {result['text']}\n")
